Package: ggbothbar
Type: Package
Title: Visualise isotopic abundance data.
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Hiedehito", "Okada", , "hidefungi@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-3210-2736"))
  )
Description: This package provides functions to visualize isotopic abundance data,
    particularly for mycoheterotrophic plants. It includes functions to calculate
    and plot standard errors and enrichment factors, and custom ggplot2 geoms for 
    error bars with various error calculation methods.
